<P>
Photo, Gaylord Perry, a college coach in South Carolina these days, cranked up 
his arm again for recent old-timers event. RICHARD KOEHLER / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Gaylord Perry was 21-6 for the Padres in 1978, 12-11 the following 
season. JOE KENNEDY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
