VIOLATIONS; HOUSING -- LOS ANGELES; REAL ESTATE INDUSTRY -- LOS ANGELES; REAL 
ESTATE INVESTMENT; REAL ESTATE FRAUD; RACKETEERING; IMMIGRANTS -- HOUSING; 
LANDLORDS; INVESTORS; MORTGAGES; LOS ANGELES -- SUITS; SHARMA, VIJAYNAND; BEN 
HORIN, MORDEHAI 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
